20: 2. READ gitnexus://repo/{name}/context             → Codebase overview, check staleness
21: 3. query({search_query: "<what you want to understand>"})  → Find related execution flows
22: 4. context({name: "<symbol>"})            → Deep dive on specific symbol
23: 5. READ gitnexus://repo/{name}/process/{name}      → Trace full execution flow
24: ```
