31: - [ ] READ gitnexus://repo/{name}/context
32: - [ ] query for the concept you want to understand
33: - [ ] Review returned processes (execution flows)
34: - [ ] context on key symbols for callers/callees
35: - [ ] READ process resource for full execution traces
