38: 
39: ## Resources
40: 
41: | Resource                                | What you get                                            |
42: | --------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
43: | `gitnexus://repo/{name}/context`        | Stats, staleness warning (~150 tokens)                  |
44: | `gitnexus://repo/{name}/clusters`       | All functional areas with cohesion scores (~300 tokens) |
45: | `gitnexus://repo/{name}/cluster/{name}` | Area members with file paths (~500 tokens)              |
46: | `gitnexus://repo/{name}/process/{name}` | Step-by-step execution trace (~200 tokens)              |
