69: ```
70: 1. READ gitnexus://repo/my-app/context       → 918 symbols, 45 processes
71: 2. query({search_query: "payment processing"})
72:    → CheckoutFlow: processPayment → validateCard → chargeStripe
73:    → RefundFlow: initiateRefund → calculateRefund → processRefund
74: 3. context({name: "processPayment"})
75:    → Incoming: checkoutHandler, webhookHandler
76:    → Outgoing: validateCard, chargeStripe, saveTransaction
77: 4. Read src/payments/processor.ts for implementation details
78: ```
