27542: 14600: 10141:  1: # Cross Memory Reasoning
27543: 14601: 10142:  2: 
27544: 14602: 10143:  3: Used when a query touches multiple domains.
27545: 14603: 10144:  4: 
27546: 14604: 10145:  5: Example:
27547: 14605: 10146:  6: 
27548: 14606: 10147:  7: - code + SLA
