27550: 14608: 10149:  9: - docs + business
27551: 14609: 10150: 10: 
27552: 14610: 10151: 11: Process:
27553: 14611: 10152: 12: 
27554: 14612: 10153: 13: 1. Query each memory
27555: 14613: 10154: 14: 2. Extract relevant signals
27556: 14614: 10155: 15: 3. Merge into unified response
27557: 14615: 10156: 16: 4. If source is code, resolve symbols via CodeGraph before broad file reads
27558: 14616: 10157: 17: 5. Register reusable pattern in code-memory feedback loop
