27956: 15014: 10555: <file path="observability/metrics.md">
27957: 15015: 10556:  1: # Metrics
27958: 15016: 10557:  2: 
27959: 15017: 10558:  3: Métricas: routing accuracy, tool usage, tool misuse, tool switching, grounding quality, gaps, token efficiency, caveman effectiveness.
27960: 15018: 10559:  4: 
27961: 15019: 10560:  5: ## Optimization Metrics
27962: 15020: 10561:  6: 
27963: 15021: 10562:  7: ### Token Saver effectiveness
27964: 15022: 10563:  8: 
27965: 15023: 10564:  9: - reduced_context_used: true/false
27966: 15024: 10565: 10: - full_file_reads_avoided
27967: 15025: 10566: 11: - chunks_retrieved
27968: 15026: 10567: 12: - tool_calls_count
27969: 15027: 10568: 13: - fallback_used
27970: 15028: 10569: 14: 
27971: 15029: 10570: 15: ### Caveman effectiveness
27972: 15030: 10571: 16: 
27973: 15031: 10572: 17: - response_mode: lite/full/evidence-first/didactic-lite
27974: 15032: 10573: 18: - unnecessary_intro_removed: true/false
27975: 15033: 10574: 19: - sources_preserved: true/false
27976: 15034: 10575: 20: - user_requested_more_detail: true/false
27977: 15035: 10576: 21: 
27978: 15036: 10577: 22: ## Umbrales operativos recomendados
27979: 15037: 10578: 23: 
27980: 15038: 10579: 24: - routing_accuracy: `>= 95%`
27981: 15039: 10580: 25: - grounding_quality (casos con fuentes): `>= 90%`
27982: 15040: 10581: 26: - tool_misuse: `<= 2%`
27983: 15041: 10582: 27: - fallback_rate: `<= 10%` (si supera, revisar reglas)
27984: 15042: 10583: 28: - token_efficiency: tendencia estable o mejorando
27985: 15043: 10584: 29: - caveman_effectiveness: `>= 85%`
27986: 15044: 10585: 30: 
27987: 15045: 10586: 31: ## Semaforo
27988: 15046: 10587: 32: 
27989: 15047: 10588: 33: - `OK`: todos los umbrales en rango.
27990: 15048: 10589: 34: - `WARN`: 1-2 metricas fuera de rango.
27991: 15049: 10590: 35: - `FAIL`: 3+ metricas fuera de rango o fallo repetido de grounding/HITL.
