29673: 16731: 22: ## Campos clave de salida
29674: 16732: 23: 
29675: 16733: 24: - `agent`
29676: 16734: 25: - `engine`
29677: 16735: 26: - `capability`
29678: 16736: 27: - `prompt.selected`
