37022: 24080:  1: # Repo Intake Eval Cases
37023: 24081:  2: 
37024: 24082:  3: Casos minimos para validar que el intake registra capacidades y dominios esperados.
37025: 24083:  4: 
37026: 24084:  5: ## Matriz base
37027: 24085:  6: 
37028: 24086:  7: 1. `boostDBA` -> `domain=dba`, motor esperado `Graphify`.
37029: 24087:  8: 1. `boost_azure_rag` -> `domain=azure-rag`, motor esperado `Azure RAG Builder`.
37030: 24088:  9: 1. `boost_iot` -> `domain=iot`, agente esperado `iot-agent`.
37031: 24089: 10: 
37032: 24090: 11: ## Criterios de aprobacion
37033: 24091: 12: 
37034: 24092: 13: 1. Repo aparece en `repo-registry/repos.yml` con `approval.status=approved`.
37035: 24093: 14: 1. Se genera capability en `repo-intake/generated/v2/<slug>/<version>/capabilities/capability.json`.
37036: 24094: 15: 1. No hay errores en `validate-repo-registry.ps1 -Strict`.
37037: 24095: 16: 
37038: 24096: 17: ## Comandos
37039: 24097: 18: 
37040: 24098: 19: ```powershell
37041: 24099: 20: pwsh -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\scripts\intake\validate-repo-registry.ps1 -Strict
37042: 24100: 21: .\scripts\intake\run-repo-intake.ps1
37043: 24101: 22: ```
37044: 24102: </file>
37045: 24103: <file path="observability/evals/routing-eval-cases.md">
